OL,3,CChannel Islands to tax large companies
OL,4,Cmore under global initiative
OL,6,Fgovernment says the island needs to
OL,7,F"play its part" in introducing a new
OL,8,Ftax for the largest multinational
OL,9,Fcompanies.
OL,11,FThe Crown Dependencies last week
OL,12,Fconfirmed they would implement the
OL,13,F'pillar two' tax, which is designed to
OL,14,Fcreate a level playing field across
OL,15,Fmore than 130 jurisdictions.
OL,17,FIt is being led by the OECD, an
OL,18,Forganisation that works with
OL,19,Fgovernments around the world to
OL,20,Fdevelop economic policy.
