OL,3,CChannel Islands to tax large companies
OL,4,Cmore under global initiative
OL,6,FThe changes would mean companies based
OL,7,Fin the islands with a turnover of more
OL,8,Fthan E750 million euros would be taxed
OL,9,Fat 15% from 2025.
OL,11,FGuernsey estimates it could bring in
OL,12,Fmore than #30 million, while Jersey is
OL,13,Fcarrying out an economic assessment
OL,14,Fwith an initial figure expected in the
OL,15,FGovernment Plan in July.
