OL,3,CChannel Islands to tax large companies
OL,4,Cmore under global initiative
OL,6,FJersey currently does not have a
OL,7,Fcorporate tax but certain financial
OL,8,Fservices companies are taxed at 10%,
OL,9,Futility companies at 20%, and retail
OL,10,Fcompanies with more than #2 million in
OL,11,Fturnover face tariffs up to 20%.
OL,13,FGuernsey similarly has a 0% standard
OL,14,Frate of company tax but does levy some
OL,15,Findustries at 10% and 20%.
