OL,3,CChannel Islands to tax large companies
OL,4,Cmore under global initiative
OL,6,FDeputy Gorst explained: "There are
OL,7,Fmany reasons why Jersey is competitive
OL,8,Fand attractive to large multinational
OL,9,Fcompanies and we will make sure that
OL,10,Fwe continue to be."
OL,12,FAnnouncing Guernsey's plans last week,
OL,13,FChief Minister Deputy Lyndon Trott
OL,14,Fsaid: "Guernsey wants to provide
OL,15,Fcertainty and stability for businesses
OL,16,Fin the island, ensuring Guernsey
OL,17,Fremains competitive while staying at
OL,18,Fthe forefront of emerging global norms
OL,19,Fin tax matters."
