OL,3,CChannel Islands to tax large companies
OL,4,Cmore under global initiative
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Locate Guernsey publicises
OL,7,Fthe fact it is a "low tax
OL,8,Fjurisdiction".
OL,10,FSo the question is, does introducing
OL,11,Fthis tax damage that selling point?
OL,13,FThe key thing to remember is few
OL,14,Fbusinesses really will be affected by
OL,15,Fit - there are 40,000 in Jersey so
OL,16,Fjust around 3.5% will face the tax.
OL,18,FIt will also enhance the islands'
OL,19,Freputations, as it is a sign they are
OL,20,Ffollowing international tax norms.
