OL,6,FFinally, it has the potential to bring
OL,7,Fin significant domestic revenues that
OL,8,Fcould help budgets in Jersey and
OL,9,FGuernsey.
OL,11,FBut it does mark a major moment for
OL,12,Fthese international finance centres,
OL,13,Fas many countries in the world seek to
OL,14,Fbecome more closely aligned in their
OL,15,Ftax policy.
